{"tid":1827314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢新型冠狀病毒肺炎新增一宗死亡個案","createTime":"2020-01-17T01:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T01:54:44.000Z","uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"375e86b3f81a570dce6b2a741e1f355f6a282dcb","tid":1827314,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T01:04:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=377040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377040&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=96958f2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377040&h=c9850cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=377040</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】武漢市衞健委表示累計新型冠狀病毒肺炎病例有41宗，新增一宗死亡個案。<br />\n<br />\n武漢市衞健委周四深夜發稿，公布一宗新增死亡個案，死者是一名69歲男子，去年12月31日病發，1月4日病情加重，轉入武漢市金銀潭醫院，入院時有嚴重心肌炎，腎功能異常，多個器官功能受損嚴重，胸部電腦掃描顯示有肺纖維病灶及胸水，懷疑有肺結核或胸膜結核，周三搶救無效不治。<br />\n<br />\n而武漢市累計的新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案有41宗，12人出院，5人情況嚴重，其餘患者情況穩定，有644人解除醫學觀察，其餘正接受醫學觀察的119名密切接觸者，暫未發現相關病例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28d3555525d01b71d19a927a2d62f3071262dc2","tid":1827314,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T01:54:44.000Z","msg":"死一個<br />\n但公佈得出黎即係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}